vernac_cmds: Definition approx (n:nat) (p:predicate) : predicate := fun w => if le_gt_dec n (level w) then T_bot else p w.
Axiom squash_unsquash : forall x, squash (unsquash x) = x.
Axiom unsquash_squash : forall n x', unsquash (squash (n,x')) = (n,fmap F (approx n) x').
Axiom knot_level : forall k:knot, level k = fst (unsquash k).
Axiom knot_age1 : forall k:knot, age1 k = match unsquash k with | (O,_) => None | (S n,x) => Some (squash (n,x)) end.
Module Knot (TF':TY_FUNCTOR) : KNOT with Module TF:=TF'.
Inductive leT : T -> T -> Prop := | leT_refl : forall t, leT t t | leT_bot: forall t, leT T_bot t.
Lemma leT_asym: forall t t', leT t t' -> leT t' t -> t = t'.
Fixpoint sinv (n: nat) : Type := match n with | O => unit | S n => prodT (sinv n) ((F (sinv n) * other) -> T) end.
Fixpoint floor (m:nat) (n:nat) (p:sinv (m+n)) : sinv n := match m as m' return forall (p : sinv (m'+n)), sinv n with | O => fun p => p | S m' => fun p => floor m' n (fst p) end p.
Fixpoint stratify (n:nat) (Q:predicate) {struct n} : sinv n := match n as n' return sinv n' with | O => tt | S n' => ( stratify n' Q, fun v => Q (existT (F oo sinv) n' (fst v),snd v) ) end.
Lemma decompose_nat : forall (x y:nat), { m:nat & y = (m + S x) } + { ge x y }.
intros x y; revert x; induction y; simpl; intros.

Definition unstratify (n:nat) (p:sinv n) : predicate := fun w => match w with (existT _ nw w',e) => match decompose_nat nw n with | inleft (existT _ m Hm) => snd (floor m (S nw) (eq_rect n _ p (m + S nw) Hm)) (w', e) | inright H => T_bot end end.
Lemma floor_shuffle: forall (m1 n : nat) (p1 : sinv (m1 + S n)) (H1 : (m1 + S n) = (S m1 + n)), floor (S m1) n (eq_rect (m1 + S n) sinv p1 (S m1 + n) H1) = fst (floor m1 (S n) p1).
remember (fst (floor m1 (S n) p1)) as p.
revert n p1 H1 p Heqp.
replace H1 with (refl_equal (S n)) by (apply proof_irr_nat); simpl; auto.
assert (m1 + S n = S m1 + n) by omega.
generalize (IHm1 n p1 H p Heqp).
replace H1 with (refl_equal (S (S (m1 + n)))) by (apply proof_irr_nat).
replace H0 with (refl_equal (S (m1+n))) in H2 by (apply proof_irr_nat).
Lemma stratify_unstratify_more : forall n m1 m2 p1 p2, floor m1 n p1 = floor m2 n p2 -> (stratify n oo unstratify (m1+n)) p1 = (stratify n oo unstratify (m2+n)) p2.
unfold compose; induction n; simpl; intros; auto.
assert ((m1 + S n) = (S m1 + n)) by omega.
assert ((m2 + S n) = (S m2 + n)) by omega.
assert (floor (S m1) n (eq_rect (m1 + S n) _ p1 _ H0) = floor (S m2) n (eq_rect (m2 + S n) _ p2 _ H1)).
replace H1 with (refl_equal (S m1 + n)) by (apply proof_irr_nat).
replace H2 with (refl_equal (S m2 + n)) by (apply proof_irr_nat).
destruct (decompose_nat n (m2 + S n)) as [[r Hr]|Hr].
destruct (decompose_nat n (m1 + S n)) as [[s Hs]|Hs].
assert (m2 = r) by omega; subst r.
assert (m1 = s) by omega; subst s.
replace Hr with (refl_equal (m2 + S n)) by (apply proof_irr_nat).
replace Hs with (refl_equal (m1 + S n)) by (apply proof_irr_nat).
Lemma stratify_unstratify : forall n, stratify n oo unstratify n = id (sinv n).
unfold id, compose; intro n; extensionality p; revert n p.
replace (stratify n (unstratify (S n) (p,f))) with (stratify n (unstratify n p)); auto.
replace (stratify n (unstratify n p)) with ((stratify n oo unstratify (0+n)) p) by trivial.
destruct (decompose_nat n (S n)) as [[r Hr]|?]; auto.
assert (r = O) by omega; subst r.
replace Hr with (refl_equal (S n)) by (apply proof_irr_nat); simpl; auto.
Lemma unstratify_stratify1 : forall n (p:predicate) w, leT ((unstratify n oo stratify n) p w) (p w).
unfold compose; induction n; simpl; intros; unfold unstratify.
case_eq w; intros nw rm Hrm.
destruct (decompose_nat nw (S n)) as [[r Hr]|?]; try (apply lt_rhs_top).
replace Hr with (refl_equal (S n)) by apply proof_irr_nat; simpl.
assert (n = r + S nw) by omega.
replace Hr with (refl_equal (S (r+S nw))) by apply proof_irr_nat; simpl.
destruct (decompose_nat nw (r + S nw)) as [[x Hx]|?].
assert (x = r) by omega; subst x.
replace Hx with (refl_equal (r + S nw)) by apply proof_irr_nat.
Lemma unstratify_stratify2 : forall n p w, projT1 (fst w) < n -> leT (p w) ((unstratify n oo stratify n) p w).
case_eq w; intros [m rm] e Hw.
assert (n = r + S m) by omega.
replace Hr with (refl_equal (S (r+S m))) by apply proof_irr_nat; simpl.
destruct (decompose_nat m (r + S m)) as [[x Hx]|?].
assert (x = r) by omega; subst x.
replace Hx with (refl_equal (r + S m)) by apply proof_irr_nat.
Lemma unstratify_stratify3 : forall n (p:predicate) w, projT1 (fst w) >= n -> leT ((unstratify n oo stratify n) p w) T_bot.
unfold compose, unstratify; intros n p w H.
rewrite Hrm in H; simpl in H.
Definition squash (x:nat * F predicate) : knot := match x with (n,y) => existT (F oo sinv) n (fmap F (stratify n) y) end.
Definition unsquash (x:knot) : (nat * F predicate) := match x with existT _ n y => (n, fmap F (unstratify n) y) end.
Definition def_knot_age1 (k:knot) : option knot := match unsquash k with | (O,_) => None | (S n,x) => Some (squash (n,x)) end.
Definition def_knot_unage (k:knot) : knot := match unsquash k with | (n,x) => squash (S n,x) end.
Definition approx (n:nat) (p:predicate) : predicate := fun w => if le_gt_dec n (def_knot_level (fst w)) then T_bot else p w.
Lemma squash_unsquash : forall x, squash (unsquash x) = x.
intros; destruct x as [x f]; simpl.
replace (fmap F (stratify x) (fmap F (unstratify x) f)) with ((fmap F (stratify x) oo fmap F (unstratify x)) f) by trivial.
replace (stratify x oo unstratify x) with (id (sinv x)).
replace (stratify x (unstratify x z)) with ((stratify x oo unstratify x) z) by trivial.
Lemma unsquash_squash : forall n x', unsquash (squash (n,x')) = (n,fmap F (approx n) x').
replace (fmap F (unstratify n) (fmap F (stratify n) x')) with ((fmap F (unstratify n) oo fmap F (stratify n)) x') by trivial.
replace (unstratify n oo stratify n) with (approx n); auto.
replace (approx n p (a, b)) with T_bot.
replace (approx n p (a, b)) with T_bot.
replace (approx n p (a, b)) with (p (a, b)).
Lemma unsquash_inj : forall k1 k2, unsquash k1 = unsquash k2 -> k1 = k2.
Lemma ag_knot_facts : ageable_facts knot def_knot_level def_knot_age1.
unfold def_knot_age1; unfold def_knot_level; simpl; intros x'.
exists (squash (S n, fmap F (unstratify n) xx')).
transitivity ((fmap F (stratify n) oo fmap F (approx (S n)) oo fmap F (unstratify n)) xx'); auto.
replace (stratify n oo approx (S n) oo unstratify n) with (@id (sinv n)).
destruct n; inv H; simpl; auto.
Definition ag_knot : ageable knot := mkAgeable knot def_knot_level def_knot_age1 ag_knot_facts .
Lemma knot_level : forall k:knot, level k = fst (unsquash k).
Lemma knot_age1 : forall k:knot, age1 k = match unsquash k with | (O,_) => None | (S n,x) => Some (squash (n,x)) end.
